<style>
  .article_column-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  img.article_column-image {
    overflow: hidden;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
  }
  .article_column-image-border {
    border: 1px solid rgba(60, 31, 27, 0.30);
  }
  .article_column {
      height: max-content;
  }
  .article_column-third {
    width: calc(33.3333334% - 33.3333334px);
  }
  .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 25px);
  }
  .article_column-text-third-top {
    padding-top: 81px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 15px);
  }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .article_column-third {
        width: calc(50% - 15px);
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 81px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 950px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .article_column-half {
      width: 100%
    }
    .article_column-third {
        width: 100%;
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .rebranding_container {
        gap: 40px;
    }
    .article_column-text .h3-heading-pp, .article_column-text .h3-heading-ss {
        text-align: center;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 450px) {
    .article_column-image {
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
      Identifying authentic Saint Laurent bags 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
        by interior logo panel
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="body-text block-max-width">
      Identifying authentic Saint Laurent bags requires a keen eye for detail and a thorough understanding of the brand’s design elements. Here are some key features to look for when identifying an authentic Saint Laurent bag:
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-center">
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "ysl-seo_interior-logo-1.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authenticating Saint Laurent bags by Interior brand tags">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Interior brand tags:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
         Authentic Saint Laurent bags feature high-quality interior brand tags made of luxurious materials. The Saint Laurent logo on these tags should be clear, precise, and well-crafted. Additionally, the logo and date codes should feature a consistent font and size, emphasizing uniformity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "ysl-seo_interior-logo-2.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authenticating Saint Laurent bags by Hardware">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Hardware:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Saint Laurent bags are renowned for their high-quality hardware, including zippers, buckles, and clasps. Authentic bags will have hardware that is sturdy, well-made, and often engraved with the Saint Laurent logo. The engravings should have letters and numbers with equal distance between each digit, highlighting the attention to detail.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-third block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <img class="article_column-image back-image-style" src="{{ "ysl-seo_interior-logo-3.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authenticating Saint Laurent bags by Overall construction">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center tac">
        <h3 class="article_column-title h3-heading-pp w-100">Overall construction:</h3>
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Authentic Saint Laurent bags are crafted with high-quality materials and exceptional craftsmanship. The construction should be sturdy, with attention to detail and a focus on quality, ensuring the bag’s durability and elegance. Some styles may utilize all capital letters in their date codes, which is a rare but notable feature.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Article Three columns",
    "class": "article_columns article_three-columns rebranding-wider-section-bottom",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}